     "data": {
      "text/markdown": [
       "# Observation of steps in gamma-ray light curves\n",
       "\n",
       "By a \"step\" we mean a change, typically around a factor or two in flux, within a short time, typically a few weeks, that is sustained for a long time, typically years."
      ],
      "text/plain": [
       "<utilities.ipynb_docgen.doc_formatter.<locals>.MimeBundleObject at 0xfcdbcdad3260>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "text/markdown": [
       "<h5 style=\"text-align:right; margin-right:15px\"> 2026-03-20 14:31</h5>"
      ],
      "text/plain": [
       "<utilities.ipynb_docgen.doc_formatter.<locals>.MimeBundleObject at 0xfcdb75391c10>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "text/markdown": [
       "## Load light curve data\n",
       "Note that the file `source_info_v3.pkl`, used here was copied from SLAC's s3df,\n",
       "where is was last updated on Jun  6 2025. \n",
       "It can be found at `/sdf/home/b/burnett/work/bb_light_curves/files`."
      ],
      "text/plain": [
       "<utilities.ipynb_docgen.doc_formatter.<locals>.MimeBundleObject at 0xfcdb74a41940>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
